data.description: Don’t miss this cozy, 3 bedroom/2 bath home! The open floor plan connects the dining room and kitchen, making it practical for everyday living and gatherings. This home features a spacious backyard, perfect for outdoor activities. Convenience is key with this location close to Downtown Houston, off of Hwy 288 and 610, the Houston Medical Center is just a 10-minute drive away. You'll find the Houston Zoo 10 minutes away, and NRG Stadium is an 8-minute drive. Travelers will appreciate being only 20 minutes from the Hobby Airport. It's been recently updated to offer modern comfort while retaining its charm. Updates include fresh paint, a new patio deck at the front entrance, updated cabinets, and granite countertops in the kitchen. The bedrooms have recently replaced carpet, while laminate floors fill the rest of the home. This home is ready for immediate move-in, so you can start enjoying your new chapter without delay. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours!
